data.description: Come make this Keller ISD Park Glen neighborhood home yours! This spacious floor plan offers formal dining, living, updated kitchen with breakfast nook, 4 bedrooms, 2 and a half baths, with a 2nd living space upstairs. The updated kitchen features emerald subway tile backsplash, new light fixtures, stainless steel appliances, and quartz countertops! Relax in the fully updated master bath featuring double vanity sinks, oversized shower, free standing tub, and walk-in closet with custom built-ins. Don't miss the large natural stone covered patio with a gas line for outdoor kitchen, the perfect spot to hang out or for entertaining! This home is walking distance to Bluebonnet elementary school. Other notable details:new HVAC system in 2022, totally redone upstairs guest bathroom, new fence on the north side, new front door, and replaced siding. Paint touch ups will be completed before closing.
